        <h3>How do I reset my password?</h3>
           <p>
               One the Sign In/Sign Up page, there is a link titled "Forgot Password?"  
               Here is the link:  <a href="http://mybuckstory.com/pwreset.html">http://mybuckstory.com/pwreset.html</a>
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>I signed up for an account, but did not receive a verification email.</h3>
           <p>
               Your email client may be sending emails generated from MyBuckStory.com to your Spam folder.  
               Check your Spam folder in your inbox, and if you see our email there, please select the email, 
               and hit the button 'Not Spam' button or link to ensure that future MyBuckStory notifications don't 
               get spammed.  Also, add 'admin@mybuckstory.com' to your contact list.
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>I'm experiencing issues with the site.  Who do I contact to get it resolved?</h3>
           <p>
               Send all notifications to <a href="mailto:admin@mybuckstory.com" title="MyBuckStory - Report a problem">admin@mybuckstory.com</a>
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>How do I edit my story?</h3>
           <p>
               Under your "My Profile" page, click on your Stories tab.  You will see the list of Stories you 
               have published.  Next to each story, there is a link to &quot;Edit this Story&quot;
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>I can't log out.  What gives?</h3>
           <p>
               Clear your browser cache - specifically your cookies.  Don't know how to do this?  Please read 
               the following article (includes videos):  
               <a href="http://www.google.com/support/accounts/bin/answer.py?hl=en&answer=32050">http://www.google.com/support/accounts/bin/answer.py?hl=en&answer=32050</a>
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>How do I post a story / edit my profile / create an event</h3>
           <p>
               Log into your account and once you are logged in there is links in the upper right of the page for you to 
               &quot;Write a Story&quot;, &quot;Edit Profile&quot;, or &quot;Create and Event&quot;
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>I have some great ideas for your site, and want to tell you about it</h3>
           <p>
               Send your ideas to <a href="mailto:admin@mybuckstory.com" title="MyBuckStory - I've got ideas for your site">admin@mybuckstory.com</a>. 
               We love to hear your ideas, and are constantly working to improve this site to make it what you want it to be.
           </p>
           <hr />
           <h3>I no longer want my free membership with MyBuckStory.com.  How do I delete my account?</h3>
           <p>
